import React from 'react';

         FormLayout,
         TextField,
         SingleOrMultuChoiceListWithChildrenContextWhenSelectedExample } from '@shopify/polaris';

export function App() {
  return (
    <Page title="Polaris">
      <Layout>
        <Layout.Section>
          <FormLayout>
            <TextField label="First name" onChange={() => {}} />
            <TextField label="Last name" onChange={() => {}} />
            <TextField label="Address" onChange={() => {}} />
            <SingleOrMultuChoiceListWithChildrenContextWhenSelectedExample />
            <TextField type="email" label="Account email" onChange={() => {}} />
            <TextField type="email" label="Account email" onChange={() => {}} />
            <TextField type="email" label="Account email" onChange={() => {}} />
            <TextField type="email" label="Account email" onChange={() => {}} />
          </FormLayout>
          <FooterHelp>
            For more details on Polaris, visit our{' '}
            <Link url="https://polaris.shopify.com">style guide</Link>.
          </FooterHelp>
        </Layout.Section>
      </Layout>
    </Page>
  );
}
